name: Pale Moon chrome mods (CCZ)
description:
A few modifications a few friends and I keep on.
  • Removes the forward button if it's disabled
  • Removes all disabled items from the context menu
    * Also removes some "annoying" items, such as "Set as Desktop Background"
  • Pretty up the about: pages
  • Minimize the yellow subscribe box on feeds (triggered on mouse-over)
additional_info:
Version: 1.0.0
Note: The only thing "Pale Moon" about this is the picture on about: pages.
